title: Model Railroader - Modeling Logging Railroads
description: Modeling a rugged logging railroad, with its tight curves, steep grades, and unique equipment, can be a rewarding experience. This package takes a look at a prototype logging railroad, the Eagle River & Northern Ry., and then explains some of the key features and terminology of the logging industry.
